WidgetTypeSelector.heading: Choose widget type from the list below
Widgets.Description.activityStream: Shows all activities occurring on the project.
Widgets.Description.bugTrend: Shows the trend of growth in the number of failed test cases from run to run.
Widgets.Description.casesTrend:
- in "Launch Mode" shows the increment of test-cases from run to run,
- in "Timeline Mode" shows the increment of test-cases distributed by dates (in launches with the largest number of test-cases per day).
Widgets.Description.cumulative: Паказвае тэндэнцыю росту зводных статыстычных дадзеных па запусках з аднолькавым ключом атрыбуту.
Widgets.Description.flakyTestCases: Shows the TOP-20 the most flaky test cases within the specified previous launches.
Widgets.Description.investigatedTrend:
- in "Launch Mode" shows whether the launches are analyzed or not (the percentage of "Investigated"/"To Investigate") from run to run,
- in "Timeline Mode" shows percentage of "Investigated"/"To Investigate" tests in all runs per day distributed by dates.
Widgets.Description.launchStatistics: Shows statistics of the last launch divided into 2 sections:</br> - Skipped, Passed, Failed </br> - Product Bug, System Issue, To Investigate, Automation Bugs.
Widgets.Description.launchesComparisonCh: Allows to compare statistics for 2 last launches side by side.
Widgets.Description.launchesDurationChar: Shows duration of the selected launches.
Widgets.Description.launchesTable: Shows the configurable table of launches.
Widgets.Description.mostFailedTestCases: Shows the TOP-20 most failing test cases within the specified previous launches.
Widgets.Description.mostTimeConsuming: show the TOP 20 the most time-consuming test cases in the last execution of the specified launch.
Widgets.Description.notPassed: Shows the percent ratio of non-passed test cases (Failed + Skipped) to Total cases from run to run.
Widgets.Description.overallStatistics: Shows summary of test cases with each statuses in the selected launches.
Widgets.Description.passingRatePerLaunch: Shows the percentage ratio of Passed test cases to Total cases for last run of selected launch.
Widgets.Description.passingRateSummary: Shows the percentage ratio of Passed test cases to Total cases for set of launches.
Widgets.Description.productStatus: Shows the configurable table that is representing launch statistics or group statistics by special filter.
Widgets.Description.statisticTrend:
- in "Launch mode" shows the growth trend in the number of test cases with each selected statuses from run to run,
- in "Timeline mode" shows sum, distributed by dates.
Widgets.Description.uniqueBugTable: Shows real identified bugs, posted to the Bug Tracking System, and existing in the BTS bugs, loaded on the project.
Widgets.Name.mostTimeConsuming: The most time-consuming test cases widget (TOP-20)
